uk.ac.ebi.pride.jmztab.utils.parser

Class PositionMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ebi.pride.jmztab.utils.parser.PositionMapping

  • public class PositionMapping
extends Object
    Create and maintain a couple of mappings between physical position and logical position. Physical position: Integer, the position of mzTab file. Logical position: String, the internal order of specification.
